# Exemplar call sequence for the hispanic-latino-stem-us benchmark.
# Updated 2026-04-17 from the initial 5-nationality version to 12
# nationality searches after a variant comparison showed the extra 7
# searches (Argentine, Chilean, Peruvian, Guatemalan, Dominican,
# Salvadoran, Ecuadorian) add ~10 gold-IN with no precision penalty.
# See docs/topic-strategies.md for the broader pattern.
